Former Barcelona star, Jean-Clair Todibo, has revealed one Lionel Messi’s rule that every player at Camp Nou must follow. According to him, Messi must not be tackled hard or injured during training Todibo, who spent last season on loan at Bundesliga side Schalke, discussed training with the Argentina International . “We all knew that he couldn’t get injured,” Todibo told Bild. “Messi was defended very carefully in training. “I learned a lot from Messi and I even tackled him a few times, but I was careful not to hurt him.” However, it would not surprise many as to the lengths Barcelona will go to protecting their most valuable asset.